Author: davidw
Content:
Why I'm married:

Because I moved away from Silicon Valley in 2000, to Padova, Italy, where there are actually women (in proportion to men (asterisk)), young people, old people, not everyone is employed in something to do with software, and ordinary people can afford houses.
